title: Fire From Below (Full Movie) Kevin Sorbo

sources.title: Fire From Below (Full Movie) Kevin Sorbo
sources.description:
Seeking a powerful alternative energy source, wealthy industrialist, Taylor Drake, carelessly unearths a vein of pure, base lithium.When the toxic lithium reaches the earth's surface and combines with water it sets off a deadly series of events that send the military on a mission deep below the earth's surface to defuse the ticking time bomb before it kills millions.

Directed by Andrew Stevens | Jim Wynorski (as J.R. Mandish)     2009    
Starring Kevin Sorbo, GiGi Erneta
